Bildad onyiso ni Nyasaye en jaadiera


1  Eka Bildad ja-Shua nodwoko Ayub kapenje niya,


2  “Ibiro thoro weche manono kamano nyaka karang’o?


3  Nyasaye ok ng’ad buch amwor, to otimo mana gima kare.


4  Nyaka bed ni nyithindi ne oketho e nyime,

mi okumogi e yo mowinjore gi kethogi.


5  To in koro duogi ir Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto.


6  Kapo ni iler, kendo ionge gi richo,

to obiro konyi, mi odwokni mwandugi duto,


7  kendo mwandu ma obiro miyi biro bedo mang’eny, ma ok nyal pim gi mago mane olalni.


8  Parie ane, rieko mag ndalo machon,

kendo neye mane kwerewa ofwenyo.


9  Wan to, ndalowa nok ahinya, omiyo ok wanyal ng’eyo gimoro,

kendo wan ngimawa e pinyni rumo piyo mana ka tipo makadho.


10  Kuom mano, we ipuonjri kuom rieko joma chon,

mondo iyud rieko mang’eny mane gin-go.


11  Bende odundu nyalo dongo ka pi onge?

Koso togo nyalo bet kama chuodho onge?


12  Ka pi odwono, to giwang’ ka pod gitindo,

kendo ka pok giromo tiyogo.


13  Ji ma ok dew Nyasaye bende chalo gi gigo,

kendo ka giseweyo Nyasaye,

to gik ma gigeno kuomgi lal nono.


14  Gik ma gigeno kuomgi chalo gi usi, kata mana gi mbuwi.


15  Koro ka giyiengore kuom mbuwi,

to mbuwi, dikonygi adier, mak oyiech?

Koso ka gimako usi, to usi diresgi mak ochot?


16  Ji ma timbegi richo chalo gi buya,

matwi kendo dongo e ndalo chwiri,

kendo landore e puodho duto.


17  Tiendegi olawore e lwendni, kendo omako matek.


18  To ka opudhgi oko,

to onge ng’ama nyalo ng’eyo ni gisebet kanyo.


19  Mano e kaka ngimagi lal nono,

kendo moko manyien wuok kuonde mane gintie.


20  Nyasaye to ok jwang’ joma ogeno kuome,

to bende ok okony joma timbegi richo.


21  Enochak omi inyier kendo ikog gi mor,


22  to enokel wichkuot ni joma mon kodi,

kendo miech joma timbegi richo nolal nono.”

